{"id": 2805, "genre": 1001, "title": "生活中有哪些「小型变故」会让你格外沮丧？", "description": "也不是不能适应，但这些细小的变化就还让人挺不安的。（题图来自：iStock ©️CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 5405, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190220015301Z6kg1wW2BnVsjT5p.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-05T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 331008, "content": "喜欢了很久的小众歌手组合基本处于解散状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440666}, {"id": 331264, "content": "外卖丢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602012}, {"id": 331009, "content": "离家千里到学校", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601313}, {"id": 331266, "content": "喜欢的男孩有了别的男孩子🙁", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602022}, {"id": 331011, "content": "睡前头发没油，起床发现头发油了贴头皮，后悔昨晚一时偷懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601312}, {"id": 331267, "content": "工资没有准时发", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410915}, {"id": 333571, "content": "自己不被人待见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549335}, {"id": 331012, "content": "宠物丢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1430010}, {"id": 331524, "content": "想要点的外卖不在配送范围。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599618}, {"id": 331269, "content": "钥匙丢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602030}, {"id": 331270, "content": "考试失败了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1521780}, {"id": 331015, "content": "腰围又大了，没合适的衣服穿了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1401626}, {"id": 331271, "content": "地铁上被性骚扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632024}, {"id": 331016, "content": "刚觉得自已有喜欢的人了，发现那个男生已经有女朋友了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601318}, {"id": 331272, "content": "说好的没课 结果离开学校之后被通知调课了要去上课", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602041}, {"id": 331017, "content": "好奇心开屏突然多了五秒广告呜呜呜呜呜", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554183}, {"id": 331273, "content": "易拉罐得环扣断了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588246}, {"id": 334089, "content": "莫名其妙被学校强制扣钱.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596580}, {"id": 331018, "content": "今天计划好要做的事情被突发事件打断。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579909}, {"id": 331274, "content": "上班打卡迟到一分钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1546758}, {"id": 331019, "content": "本来要发的奖金突然说不能发到我头上了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1488266}, {"id": 331275, "content": "赤道地区野人舞娘 没发微博", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602049}, {"id": 331020, "content": "端子被封了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310502}, {"id": 331276, "content": "喜欢的女演员不拍了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1595785}, {"id": 331021, "content": "朋友突然冷淡", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599153}, {"id": 331277, "content": "说的带薪休年假，只有年假没有薪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490255}, {"id": 331022, "content": "喜欢的品牌商店停业了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1585795}, {"id": 331278, "content": "约好的聚会取消了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1399351}, {"id": 331534, "content": "喜欢的动漫/电影/音乐突然开始收费", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467674}, {"id": 331023, "content": "喜欢吃的食物突然不卖了，", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927713}, {"id": 331279, "content": "食堂二楼的黄焖鸡不开了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576347}, {"id": 331024, "content": "之前最喜欢的hqx约谈了，觉得好可怕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291669}, {"id": 331025, "content": "说了一万次要早睡，一看手机又是凌晨……", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581314}, {"id": 331281, "content": "曾经觉得我非常喜欢的一个女孩子一瞬间不喜欢了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1587473}, {"id": 335889, "content": "喜欢的网站进不去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620621}, {"id": 338449, "content": "早饭钱掉了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633869}, {"id": 331026, "content": "查无此人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1177861}, {"id": 331282, "content": "平时早上开着的早点铺在我某一天起晚的时候刚好没开", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581514}, {"id": 331027, "content": "线上精听党的英语阅读落下了一个选择题导致打卡失败，然后不返押金了😭😭", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454654}, {"id": 331283, "content": "机读卡没涂ab卷去补考了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 331795, "content": "陌生人突然真的陌生了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603328}, {"id": 331028, "content": "艾玛 大概是早上上班 错过了一趟时间吃得很紧的公交", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601347}, {"id": 331029, "content": "诚如简介 好奇葩在国内是个有风险的事情\n当你以为世界都在对你笑时 才发现原来众人早已在背地分析你的每一个环节 在众人面前你就是个透明的假人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601348}, {"id": 331285, "content": "甲方爸爸说，钱迟点转给你！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602102}, {"id": 331541, "content": "做设计电脑黑屏了！！！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1559521}, {"id": 331030, "content": "喜欢的人突然联系不到了", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601351}, {"id": 331286, "content": "早上醒来，发现今天还要去上班！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 331031, "content": "缓冲中……播放……缓冲中……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571426}, {"id": 331287, "content": "梦里是周末！醒来却要去上班！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 331032, "content": "贴子被删，想看的看不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320043}]}